								"html": "<div class=\"rounded p-6 gap-3 mt-3 bg-dark-subtle text-light\" style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\"><h2 style=\"text-align:center;\"><strong>MATH &amp; READING AFTER-SCHOOL PROGRAM</strong></h2>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t<strong>(Program is offered to 1st - 8th grade students)</strong>\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>TUTORING DAYS &amp; TIMES</strong><br>\n\tTuesdays - Thursdays<br>\n\t3:30 pm - 6:00 pm</span>\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>ADDITIONAL SERVICES</strong><br>\n\tMonthly Science Fairs and Healthy Eating Workshops<br>\n\tLed by the USC MED Students</span>\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>LOCATION</strong><br>\n\tThe Salvation Army of the Midlands<br>\n\t3024 Farrow Road, Columbia 29203</span>\n</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>FOR ADDITIONAL INFORMATION</strong><br>\n\temail: Lisa.Chandler@uss.salvationarmy.org</span>\n</p></div>",
